for Electrolyt Capacitors see also :&lt;p&gt;
www.bccomponents.com &lt;p&gt;
www.panasonic.com&lt;p&gt;
www.kemet.com&lt;p&gt;
http://www.secc.co.jp/pdf/os_e/2004/e_os_all.pdf &lt;b&gt;(SANYO)&lt;/b&gt;
